# Integration test: IIcx System 7.0.1 Floppy Boot
# Runs the Universal ROM with the System 7.0.1 floppy attached for
# enough cycles to exit SCSI scan, transfer to the System 7 boot
# blocks, and let the JMFB PrimaryInit run.

# 1B instructions: covers RAM test (~300M) + SCSI scan + Slot Manager
# probe + System 7 boot-block load + first Finder paint pass on the
# matching SE/30 path.  IIcx may need more once mode-table parsing
# inside the JMFB driver lights up.
scheduler.run 1000000000

# Machine identified.
assert ${machine.id == "iicx"} "machine.id != iicx"

# Display still on the 640x480 default — System 7's first cscSetMode
# may bump format/depth but not resolution unless the user explicitly
# changes monitor.
assert ${screen.width == 640} "screen.width != 640"
assert ${screen.height == 480} "screen.height != 480"

quit
